      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">The human body contains five liters of blood, which is made of
          several useful
          components i.e. <strong>Whole blood</strong>, <strong>Platelet</strong>, and <strong>Plasma</strong>.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">Each type of component has several medical uses and can be used
          for different
          medical treatments. your blood donation determines the best donation for you to make.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">For <strong>plasma</strong> and <strong>platelet</strong>
          donation you must
          have donated whole blood in past two years.</p>
        <br><br>
